50 turns into 150.

11
00:00:26.090 --> 00:00:28.860
Till you get to 150.
That's how the biscuit breaks.

12
00:00:29.860 --> 00:00:31.590
Are you a fucking snitch. Wes?

13
00:00:31.690 --> 00:00:33.030
