14
00:00:34.400 --> 00:00:36.300
You fucking killed him.

15
00:00:37.700 --> 00:00:39.030
You a good vet?

16
00:00:39.140 --> 00:00:41.470
I believe so. yes.

17
00:00:41.540 --> 00:00:42.640
