41
00:02:21.440 --> 00:02:22.770
Five thousand acres.

42
00:02:22.870 --> 00:02:23.970
Black Angus.

43
00:02:24.110 --> 00:02:25.640
175 head on it.

44
00:02:25.740 --> 00:02:27.410
