317
00:17:44.590 --> 00:17:45.730
Yes. ma'am.

318
00:17:45.830 --> 00:17:47.060
Good.

319
00:17:48.130 --> 00:17:49.430
You may go.

320
00:17:53.340 --> 00:17:55.470
